            <p>As someone who loves studying languages AND programming, I thought I would try my hand at app development.  The app supports the three languages that I have studied over my life: Japanese, Korean, and Chinese.</p>
        </br>
            <p>There is a Spring Boot web API hosted on Heroku, with endpoints for getting different vocabulary terms, with the ability to filter on both category (verbs, adjectives, etc.) and level (scale 1-5). This API hooks into a small MySQL database I have hosted holding information on vocabulary terms and their associated metadata.</p>


