                    <li>MySql backed app</li>
                </ul>
             </div>
            </div>

        </br>
            <p>The project was a great introduction to me with several new technologies. Building a web API backed mobile app from the bottom-up was a great learning experience. I learned a lot about the Spring Framework and dependency injection in general that I have applied at my work and in other projects.  And best off all I got a highly customizable application that I use everyday for my language learning hobby. 
